<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-01-05T21:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-05-31T23:30:00-05:00" n="1046" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d1046">
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                            </head>
                            <p>A conference of American Chiefs of Mission in Near Eastern countries
                                was held at Istanbul from November 26 to 29. The agreed conclusions
                                (see <ref target="#pg_168">page 168</ref>) embodied a ninth item
                                entitled “Current <pb facs="1527" n="1511" xml:id="pg_1511"/>
                                Israeli-Jordan Peace Negotiations and Annexation of Arab Palestine
                                to Jordan.”</p>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>